# ============================================================================
# FILE: .nojekyll
# PATH: /marisselle-teacher/.nojekyll
# PURPOSE: Disable Jekyll processing on GitHub Pages
# ============================================================================
# 
# This file tells GitHub Pages NOT to process this repository with Jekyll.
# Without this file, GitHub Pages will:
# - Ignore files and folders starting with underscore (_)
# - Treat files with front matter as Jekyll templates
# - Break API routing for /api/teacher/* endpoints
# - Prevent proper WASM/JS file serving
#
# With this file, GitHub Pages:
# - Serves ALL files as-is
# - Preserves underscore-prefixed files (_headers, _redirects)
# - Allows proper API routing
# - Enables WASM/JS serving
#
# This file should be empty - its mere existence is enough.
# ============================================================================
